{"title":"The US has Low Electricity Prices","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/896195123/0/marginalrevolution~The-US-has-Low-Electricity-Prices.html","date":1715253417000,"content":"<p>The US has some of the lowest electricity prices in the world. Shown below are <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://op.europa.eu/en/publication-detail/-/publication/3b43f47c-e1c5-11ee-8b2b-01aa75ed71a1/\">industrial retail electricity prices in EU27, USA, UK, China and Japan</a>. Electricity is critical for AI compute, electric cars and more generally reducing carbon footprints. The US needs to build much more electricity infrastructure, by some estimates <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://ifp.org/how-to-save-americas-transmission-system/\">tripling or quadrupling production</a>. That’s quite possible with <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://ifp.org/how-to-save-americas-transmission-system/\">deregulation and permitting reform</a>. I am pleased to learn, moreover, that we are starting from a better base than I had imagined.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Electricity.png\" width=\"816\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Electricity.png 816w, https://marginalrevolution.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Electricity-300x159.png 300w, https://marginalrevolution.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Electricity-768x408.png 768w\" /></p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/05/the-us-has-low-electricity-prices.html\">The US has Low Electricity Prices</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/896195123/0/marginalrevolut